OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBP faces rebel shareholders
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover new climate goals     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some of the UK's biggest pension funds 
OL,6, are to vote against reappointing BP's  
OL,7, chairman over a decision to weaken its 
OL,8, climate plans.                         
OL,10,FIt comes after the energy giant cut    
OL,11,Fback its target to reduce emissions by 
OL,12,Fthe end of the decade.                 
OL,14,FAhead of the firm's annual meeting on  
OL,15,FThursday, the five pension schemes, all
OL,16,Fshareholders in BP, criticised a       
OL,17,F"failure of governance" .              
OL,19,FBP said it valued "constructive        
OL,20,Fchallenge and engagement".             
